message.text:
𝐉𝐨𝐢𝐧 𝐔𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝐨𝐟 𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐈𝐧𝐧𝐨𝐯𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧! 

Are you ready to 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑 into the dynamic world of hospitality and tourism? 

We invite you to be part of an exciting event on:
🗓️𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟒, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 (Wednesday)
⏰ 1:00 PM-5:00 PM
📍 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐮𝐦, 𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠, 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐥𝐚

This year’s theme, 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑, “𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐩𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐨𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐛𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬𝐞𝐭”, is your chance to explore how innovation can shape our vibrant industries, brought to you by 𝐊𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐝𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬! 

Whether you’re an aspiring Entrepreneur, HRM and Tourism Students, this event is designed to inspire and equip you with the tools you need to thrive!

So, mark your calendars and prepare for a day of insightful learning and professional growth. Let's shape the future together-because the sky's the limit! 

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐧𝐨𝐰 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐛𝐞 𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐞𝐱𝐜𝐢𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭! Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity!

E-certificates will be provided to all attendees.

𝐉𝐨𝐢𝐧 𝐔𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝐨𝐟 𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐈𝐧𝐧𝐨𝐯𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧! 

Are you ready to 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑 into the dynamic world of hospitality and tourism? 

We invite you to be part of an exciting event on:
🗓️𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟒, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 (Wednesday)
⏰ 1:00 PM-5:00 PM
📍 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐮𝐦, 𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠, 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐥𝐚

This year’s theme, 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑, “𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐩𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐨𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐛𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬𝐞𝐭”, is your chance to explore how innovation can shape our vibrant industries, brought to you by 𝐊𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐝𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬! 

Whether you’re an aspiring Entrepreneur, HRM and Tourism Students, this event is designed to inspire and equip you with the tools you need to thrive!

So, mark your calendars and prepare for a day of insightful learning and professional growth. Let's shape the future together-because the sky's the limit! 

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐧𝐨𝐰 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐛𝐞 𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐞𝐱𝐜𝐢𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭! Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity!

E-certificates will be provided to all attendees.

https://forms.office.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=3F6kgO7V4EaddTfEe-m3zM3QzDs0peRLmijvCfcM1HlUNjRVQk9STTdVUU1LWTNWMUJQMlZWOEhVRS4u

message.text:
𝐉𝐨𝐢𝐧 𝐔𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝐨𝐟 𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐈𝐧𝐧𝐨𝐯𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧! 

Are you ready to 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑 into the dynamic world of hospitality and tourism? 

We invite you to be part of an exciting event on:
🗓️𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟒, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 (Wednesday)
⏰ 1:00 PM-5:00 PM
📍 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐮𝐦, 𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠, 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐥𝐚

This year’s theme, 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑, “𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐩𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐨𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐛𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬𝐞𝐭”, is your chance to explore how innovation can shape our vibrant industries, brought to you by 𝐊𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐝𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬! 

Whether you’re an aspiring Entrepreneur, HRM and Tourism Students, this event is designed to inspire and equip you with the tools you need to thrive!

So, mark your calendars and prepare for a day of insightful learning and professional growth. Let's shape the future together-because the sky's the limit! 

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐧𝐨𝐰 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐛𝐞 𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐞𝐱𝐜𝐢𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭! Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity!

E-certificates will be provided to all attendees.

https://forms.office.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=3F6kgO7V4EaddTfEe-m3zM3QzDs0peRLmijvCfcM1HlUNjRVQk9STTdVUU1LWTNWMUJQMlZWOEhVRS4u

#StartUpServeSoar
#HospitalityandTourismFuture

message.text:
𝐉𝐨𝐢𝐧 𝐔𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝐨𝐟 𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐈𝐧𝐧𝐨𝐯𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧! 

Are you ready to 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑 into the dynamic world of hospitality and tourism? 

We invite you to be part of an exciting event on:
🗓️𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟒, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 (Wednesday)
⏰ 1:00 PM-5:00 PM
📍 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐮𝐦, 𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠, 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐥𝐚

This year’s theme, 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑, “𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐩𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐨𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐛𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬𝐞𝐭”, is your chance to explore how innovation can shape our vibrant industries, brought to you by 𝐊𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐝𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬! 

Whether you’re an aspiring Entrepreneur, HRM and Tourism Students, this event is designed to inspire and equip you with the tools you need to thrive!

So, mark your calendars and prepare for a day of insightful learning and professional growth. Let's shape the future together-because the sky's the limit! 

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐧𝐨𝐰 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐛𝐞 𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐞𝐱𝐜𝐢𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭! Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity!

E-certificates will be provided to all attendees.

message.text:
𝐉𝐨𝐢𝐧 𝐔𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝐨𝐟 𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐈𝐧𝐧𝐨𝐯𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧! 

Are you ready to 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑 into the dynamic world of hospitality and tourism? 

We invite you to be part of an exciting event on:
🗓️𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟒, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 (Wednesday)
⏰ 1:00 PM-5:00 PM
📍 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐮𝐦, 𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠, 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐥𝐚

This year’s theme, 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑, “𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐩𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐨𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐛𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬𝐞𝐭”, is your chance to explore how innovation can shape our vibrant industries, brought to you by 𝐊𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐝𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬! 

Whether you’re an aspiring Entrepreneur, HRM and Tourism Students, this event is designed to inspire and equip you with the tools you need to thrive!

So, mark your calendars and prepare for a day of insightful learning and professional growth. Let's shape the future together-because the sky's the limit! 

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐧𝐨𝐰 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐛𝐞 𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐞𝐱𝐜𝐢𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭! Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity!

E-certificates will be provided to all attendees.

https://forms.office.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=3F6kgO7V4EaddTfEe-m3zM3QzDs0peRLmijvCfcM1HlUNjRVQk9STTdVUU1LWTNWMUJQMlZWOEhVRS4u

message.text:
𝐉𝐨𝐢𝐧 𝐔𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝐨𝐟 𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐈𝐧𝐧𝐨𝐯𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧! 

Are you ready to 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑 into the dynamic world of hospitality and tourism? 

We invite you to be part of an exciting event on:
🗓️𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟒, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 (Wednesday)
⏰ 1:00 PM-5:00 PM
📍 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐢 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐮𝐦, 𝐅𝐄𝐔𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐂𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠, 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐥𝐚

This year’s theme, 𝐒𝐓𝐀𝐑𝐓-𝐔𝐏, 𝐒𝐄𝐑𝐕𝐄, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐎𝐀𝐑, “𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐦𝐩𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐇𝐨𝐬𝐩𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐚 𝐆𝐥𝐨𝐛𝐚𝐥 𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐬𝐞𝐭”, is your chance to explore how innovation can shape our vibrant industries, brought to you by 𝐊𝐚𝐰𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐝𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬! 

Whether you’re an aspiring Entrepreneur, HRM and Tourism Students, this event is designed to inspire and equip you with the tools you need to thrive!

So, mark your calendars and prepare for a day of insightful learning and professional growth. Let's shape the future together-because the sky's the limit! 

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐧𝐨𝐰 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐛𝐞 𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐞𝐱𝐜𝐢𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭! Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity!

E-certificates will be provided to all attendees.

https://forms.office.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=3F6kgO7V4EaddTfEe-m3zM3QzDs0peRLmijvCfcM1HlUNjRVQk9STTdVUU1LWTNWMUJQMlZWOEhVRS4u

#StartUpServeSoar
#HospitalityandTourismFuture

message.text:
#TamAnunsyo | As of September 15, 2025, the FEU Central Student Organization has formally submitted a recommendation letter in light of the upcoming nationwide transport strike announced by PISTON and MANIBELA on September 17–19, 2025.

Grounded on the results of the recent #TamsCheck Survey, the FEUCSO emphasized the need for proactive adjustments to safeguard student welfare and academic continuity. The recommendations include:

1. Shift to Online Modality during the strike dates
2. Leniency of Attendance for affected students
3. Extended Hours of University Facilities
4. Provision of Early and Clear Announcements

Check the full recommendation letter here: 

🔗: https://bit.ly/TransportStrikeRecommendationLetter

The FEUCSO remains committed to representing the concerns of the Tamaraw community and to engaging in constructive dialogue with the University for responsive and student-centered solutions.

Stay updated through our TamAnunsyo.

#TamaRiseTogether
#FEUCSO90

Grounded on the results of the recent #TamsCheck Survey, the FEUCSO emphasized the need for proactive adjustments to safeguard student welfare and academic continuity. The recommendations include:

1. Shift to Online Modality during the strike dates
2. Leniency of Attendance for affected students
3. Extended Hours of University Facilities
4. Provision of Early and Clear Announcements

Check the full recommendation letter here: 

🔗: https://bit.ly/TransportStrikeRecommendationLetter

The FEUCSO remains committed to representing the concerns of the Tamaraw community and to engaging in constructive dialogue with the University for responsive and student-centered solutions.

Stay updated through our TamAnunsyo.

#TamaRiseTogether
#FEUCSO90

Grounded on the results of the recent #TamsCheck Survey, the FEUCSO emphasized the need for proactive adjustments to safeguard student welfare and academic continuity. The recommendations include:

1. Shift to Online Modality during the strike dates
2. Leniency of Attendance for affected students
3. Extended Hours of University Facilities
4. Provision of Early and Clear Announcements

Check the full recommendation letter here: 

🔗: https://bit.ly/TransportStrikeRecommendationLetter

The FEUCSO remains committed to representing the concerns of the Tamaraw community and to engaging in constructive dialogue with the University for responsive and student-centered solutions.

Stay updated through our TamAnunsyo.
